 />\n無 執到佢嗰陣見到係有個箱裝住 無見到附近有貓媽媽"},{"pid":"8d350926aaee8c3e2b4e59161f67dcb1084a3802","tid":299883,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T12:47:36.000Z","msg":"我見到有蚤係佢個身到 佢咁細隻應該點幫佢杜蚤"},{"pid":"2b18137381dfcc218088ab3021e583573e308599","tid":299883,"uid":111962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T12:48:09.000Z","msg":"應該兩個月 快d帶主子睇醫生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f7e5de181330a030fa2b6cc87750f99bc5c6668","tid":299883,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T12:49:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該兩個月 快d帶主子睇醫生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好的謝主隆恩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"459c4420f4bdf10b250ba313137d7d6869c480cd","tid":299883,"uid":8388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T12:51:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我見到有蚤係佢個身到 佢咁細隻應該點幫佢杜蚤</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果可以既帶去睇醫生，順便身體檢查<br />\n<br />\n貓b會多謝您的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a50baad6be242a5ed27f41df3c7ec4c8c52975c","tid":299883,"uid":47819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T12:51:25.000Z","msg":"睇相1-2個月左右<br />\n應該戒左奶...？<br />\n<br />\n如果濕糧佢肯食就畀濕糧<br />\n乾糧覺得太硬身既話可以浸林佢<br />\n乾濕糧可以同時提供 最緊要肯食<br />\n仲想要奶就畀貓奶佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝你畀個家佢"},{"pid":"b1ce2702c93060dab96883470e2a210ded86ba47","tid":299883,"uid":8388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T12:52:22.000Z","msg":"btw食到乾糧應該都唔會太細了"},{"pid":"d696b66b192f0d66bb4a80292d0e9528e19f8ce8","tid":299883,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T13:04:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我見到有蚤係佢個身到 佢咁細隻應該點幫佢杜蚤</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果可以